messages.message: A page can't contain more then one '@Entry' annotation.
The '@Consume' property 'value2' cannot be assigned to the 'regular' property 'title'.
The '@Provide' property 'value' cannot be assigned to the 'regular' property 'title1'.
The '@StoragePropRef' property 'value2' cannot be assigned to the 'regular' property 'title'.
